cript><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Cloak_of_Starlight rootpage-Cloak_of_Starlight skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\twindow.google_analytics_uacct = \"UA-3380984-8\";\n</script>\n<div class=\"adsense\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\n\t\tgoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7088061744296615\";\n\t\t/* CrawlWiki skyscraper */\n\t\tgoogle_ad_slot = \"8196155564\";\n\t\tgoogle_ad_width = 160;\n\t\tgoogle_ad_height = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Cloak of Starlight</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #33FF66; background-color: #e0fae0; border-left: 15px solid #33FF66; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.31\" title=\"0.31\">0.31</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> A phosphorescent cloak, woven of pure light beams. The ripples of its folds as the wearer leaps and swerves in combat may dazzle those who gaze on it.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><a href=\"/File:Urand_starlight.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Urand starlight.png\" src=\"/images/9/97/Urand_starlight.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <i><b>the +1 cloak of Starlight</b></i>\n</p><p>+1 <a href=\"/Cloak\" title=\"Cloak\">cloak</a><br />\ncan <a href=\"/Blind\" title=\"Blind\">Dazzle</a> attackers (20% when dodging an attack)<br />\n+4 <a href=\"/EV\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"EV\">EV</a><br />\n<a href=\"/Stealth\" title=\"Stealth\">Stealth</a>--\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Desirability\">Desirability</span></h2>\n<p>The <b>cloak of Starlight</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is usually a very competitive piece of equipment. As a +1 cloak with +4 EV, it will be better than a mundane cloak. The <a href=\"/Blind#Dazzle\" title=\"Blind\">*Dazzle</a> effect comes in handy fairly often, especially for evasive characters.\n</p><p>The stealth hit is generally not too painful; usually you either have enough stealth that it doesn't matter, or you aren't using stealth at all. <a href=\"/Stab\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stab\">Stabbers</a> might disagree when attempting to take out a sleeping <a href=\"/Unique\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Unique\">unique</a>, but in other cases the cloak provides a lot of opportunities for low-tier stabs.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>In <a href=\"/0.26\" title=\"0.26\">0.26</a>, the cloak got the *Dazzle property and lost rElec and rC+.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.19\" title=\"0.19\">0.19</a>, the cloak had a +2 enchantment.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.17\" title=\"0.17\">0.17</a>, the cloak had a +0 enchantment and lesser stealth penalty (Stlth-).</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.15\" title=\"0.15\">0.15</a>, stealth penalty was -30.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.0/crawl-ref/source/art-data.txt#L1034\">art-data.txt:1034</a> (0.30.0)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916135602\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.044 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.062 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 212/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1473/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 197/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.000s\nLua virtual size: 8.02 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   44.855      1 -total\n 79.55%   35.683      1 Template:Version031\n 76.62%   34.368      1 Template:Version\n  3.00%    1.346      1 Template:Source_ref\n  2.93%    1.313      1 Template:Flavour\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:4436-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916135602 and revision id 79252\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Cloak_of_Starlight&amp;oldid=79252\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Cloak_of_Starlight&amp;oldid=79252</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-c