div style=\"clear:both\"></div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgPageParseReport\":{\"smw\":{\"limitreport-intext-parsertime\":0},\"limitreport\":{\"cputime\":\"0.044\",\"walltime\":\"0.062\",\"ppvisitednodes\":{\"value\":57,\"limit\":1000000},\"ppgeneratednodes\":{\"value\":212,\"limit\":1000000},\"postexpandincludesize\":{\"value\":1473,\"limit\":2097152},\"templateargumentsize\":{\"value\":197,\"limit\":2097152},\"expansiondepth\":{\"value\":4,\"limit\":40},\"expensivefunctioncount\":{\"value\":0,\"limit\":100},\"timingprofile\":[\"100.00%   44.855      1 -total\",\" 79.55%   35.683      1 Template:Version031\",\" 76.62%   34.368      1 Template:Version\",\"  3.00%    1.346      1 Template:Source_ref\",\"  2.93%    1.313      1 Template:Flavour\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240916135602\",\"ttl\":86400,\"transientcontent\":false}}});});</script><script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":254});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{version031}}\n{{flavour|A phosphorescent cloak, woven of pure light beams. The ripples of its folds as the wearer leaps and swerves in combat may dazzle those who gaze on it.}}\n[[File:Urand starlight.png]] '''''the +1 cloak of Starlight'''''\n\n+1 [[cloak]]<br>\ncan [[Blind|Dazzle]] attackers (20% when dodging an attack)<br>\n+4 [[EV]]<br>\n[[Stealth]]--\n\n==Desirability==\nThe '''cloak of Starlight'''<ref>{{source ref|0.30.0|art-data.txt|1034}}</ref> is usually a very competitive piece of equipment. As a +1 cloak with +4 EV, it will be better than a mundane cloak. The [[Blind#Dazzle|*Dazzle]] effect comes in handy fairly often, especially for evasive characters.\n\nThe stealth hit is generally not too painful; usually you either have enough stealth that it doesn't matter, or you aren't using stealth at all. [[Stab]]bers might disagree when attempting to take out a sleeping [[unique]], but in other cases the cloak provides a lot of opportunities for low-tier stabs.\n\n==History==\n*In [[0.26]], the cloak got the *Dazzle property and lost rElec and rC+.\n*Prior to [[0.19]], the cloak had a +2 enchantment.\n*Prior to [[0.17]], the cloak had a +0 enchantment and lesser stealth penalty (Stlth-).\n*Prior to [[0.15]], stealth penalty was -30.\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n[[Category:Unrands]]\n[[Category:Cloaks]]"}